The experience gained in Azerbaijan in the field of multiculturalism is very interesting to all of us.
Over the centuries, representatives of different religions, nations have lived in Azerbaijan as a family.
There has never been any confrontation or confusion on religious or ethnic grounds in Azerbaijan, and I am convinced that it will not.
Educational society is a driving force behind it. Intellectual potential will determine the development of each country today and especially in the future.
There are countries, rich natural resources. However, because of the low intellectual level, those countries can not achieve sustainable development.
To transform our natural resources in Azerbaijan, first of all, into intellectual potential (cont) http://t.co/dHrenNNe

We see that if there is a modern approach, there will be immediate progress and tendencies towards progress.
National and spiritual values ​​play a special role in the globalizing world, especially for the younger generation.

Therefore, in these globalized worlds, special attention should be paid to these issues, because today we are experiencing rapid scientific and technological progress.
New technologies, internet and other technologies are very important to us, and Azerbaijan has achieved great success in this area.
We want the young generation to grow up in the spirit of patriotism, in the spirit of respect for their history and culture, in the spirit of national spirit.
